OL,3,CRegional divide as house prices came
OL,4,Cunder increased pressure in April `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHouse prices came under increased
OL,8,Fpressure in April, with signs of a
OL,9,Fwidening regional divide, according to
OL,10,Fsurveyors.
OL,12,FA net balance of 34% of property
OL,13,Fprofessionals reported house prices
OL,14,Ffalling rather than rising,
OL,15,Fdeteriorating from a balance of 25% of
OL,16,Fprofessionals who saw this in March,
OL,17,Fthe Royal Institution of Chartered
OL,18,FSurveyors (RICS) said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
