FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30702
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778724214
OL,3,CRegional divide as house prices came
OL,4,Cunder increased pressure in April `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FThe report highlighted a widening
OL,8,Fdivide, with stronger downward
OL,9,Fpressure on prices reported in London,
OL,10,Fthe South East, East Anglia and the
OL,11,FSouth West.
OL,13,FIn northern England, house prices were
OL,14,Fstill "marginally positive" while
OL,15,Fprices were also still increasing in
OL,16,FScotland and Northern Ireland, RICS
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,26,@vD@GOUvD@[O]
