SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778724214
OL,3,CRegional divide as house prices came
OL,4,Cunder increased pressure in April `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FHigher mortgage rates continued to
OL,8,Fdampen home buyer demand in April,
OL,9,Fwith signs that the conflict in the
OL,10,FMiddle East is also affecting
OL,11,Fconfidence, the report added.
OL,13,FA net balance of 34% of professionals
OL,14,Freported new buyer inquiries falling
OL,15,Frather than rising.
OL,17,FAgreed sales also remained weak, with
OL,18,Fa net balance of 36% of professionals
OL,19,Fseeing falls.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778724214
OL,3,CRegional divide as house prices came
OL,4,Cunder increased pressure in April `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FExpectations among professionals for
OL,8,Fsales in the months ahead were also
OL,9,Fsubdued, but were less negative for 12
OL,10,Fmonths' time compared with the next
OL,11,Fthree months, the research indicated.
OL,13,FRICS said there were also signs the
OL,14,Fpipeline of homes being listed may
OL,15,Fweaken.
OL,17,FThe rental market continued to show
OL,18,Fdemand outpacing supply, with tenant
OL,19,Fdemand rising while landlord
OL,20,Finstructions fell.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
