FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778724214
OL,3,CRegional divide as house prices came
OL,4,Cunder increased pressure in April `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,FTarrant Parsons, head of market
OL,8,Fresearch and analysis at RICS, said:
OL,9,F"April's results show a housing market
OL,10,Fstill in the grip of macro headwinds
OL,11,Fstemming from the Middle East conflict.
OL,13,F"Recent warnings from the Bank of
OL,14,FEngland that interest rate rises may
OL,15,Fbe required to tackle renewed
OL,16,Finflation, driven by elevated oil
OL,17,Fprices and disrupted supply chains,
OL,18,Funderline the challenging environment
OL,19,Ffacing buyers.
OL,26,@qD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
