OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,308,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30706
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F307A1778724214
OL,3,CRegional divide as house prices came
OL,4,Cunder increased pressure in April `
OL,5,Creport
OL,7,F"Until there is a clearer path for
OL,8,Finflation and borrowing costs,
OL,9,Factivity and sentiment look set to
OL,10,Fremain subdued, particularly across
OL,11,Fsouthern England and London where
OL,12,Faffordability pressures are most
OL,13,Facute."
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@GO]
